content:
CRM Analytics gives you multiple ways to get insights on the go: CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app and CRM Analytics for iOS and Android. Find out which mobile experience is right for you.

The right mobile analytics experience depends on what you want to do.

For the best mobile analytics experience in the CRM workflow, use CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app.
For the most focused analytics on-the-go experience, use CRM Analytics for iOS or Android.

Check out this breakdown of key CRM Analytics features based on business needs.

BUSINESS NEED	CRM ANALYTICS FOR IOS	CRM ANALYTICS FOR ANDROID	SALESFORCE APP (IOS AND ANDROID)

Want to add mobile-optimized insights to a record page? Use CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app.
Want to take action on insights directly from CRM Analytics? Use CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app.
Want to launch analytics dashboards from a Salesforce record page? Use CRM Analytics in the Salesforce app.
Want to explore data and uncover key business insights on your mobile device? Use CRM Analytics for iOS or Android.
Want to launch analytics assets directly from your own custom mobile app? Use CRM Analytics for iOS or Android.
Want to view and analyze data when internet access isnâ€™t available? Use CRM Analytics for iOS.
Want to track important metrics in your Watchlist? Access it in CRM Analytics for iOS.
Want to get notified when a metric reaches a goal or dips below a specified amount? Use CRM Analytics for iOS.
title: Choosing the Right CRM Analytics Mobile Experience
